From: Tana Jones on 11/30/2000 03:54 PM
To: Kal Shah/HOU/ECT@ECT
cc:  
Subject: Re: Unilateral confidentiality agreement  

Does Dr. Batsell's company have a name?



	Kal Shah
	11/30/2000 03:18 PM
		 
		 To: Tana Jones/HOU/ECT@ECT
		 cc: Dave Samuels/HOU/ECT@ECT
		 Subject: Unilateral confidentiality agreement

Tana -- Per our conversation, I need a unilateral confidentiality agreement 
for:

Analytica, Inc.
Attention:  Dr. Richard R. Batsell
3601 Plumb
Houston TX 77005-2929

email:  Randy@batsell.com
fax:  713 669 1017
phone:  713 661 6878

I am going to discuss the possibility of having Dr. Batsell's company conduct 
a market research study on electronic commerce platforms.  The results of the 
study will be used by EnronOnline management in strategy formulation.  

You can fax or e-mail the agreement directly to Dr. Batsell.

Thanks

Kal
